s makes our future life as though yet to be exist.Human mind can't yet perceive the nature of future.\n\n- Toba Beta, My Ancestor Was an Ancient Astronaut\n|\nWorthy or not, you will receive your destiny. Awake or not you will notice.\n\n- Julieanne\n|\nthe problems changed, but people were the same\n\n- Dorothy Gilman, The Elusive Mrs. Pollifax\n|\nA dream is a scripture, and many scriptures are nothing but dreams.\n\n- Umberto\n|\nYou have the right to chose your destiny, otherwise you will be left to live someone else's idea of what your life should be.\n\n- Steven Redhead, The Solution\n|\nLike all young people, you are quite sure that you alone feel and think, you alone recognize danger, you alone are the only one clever enough to realise...\n\n- J.K. Rowling, Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix\n|\nIf nominated, I will not run; if elected, I will not serve.\n\n- William\n|\nHuman communication and literature are all made of words; thus, it’s hard to overestimate their unbelievable power.\n\n- Sahara\n|\nDon Quixote's misfortune is not his imagination, but Sancho Panza.\n\n- Franz\n|\nI found there are many things women ask for in a love. Other women demand money, power, or adventure. All I pray for is that he is patient, and plead that he will love me.\n\n- R. Y.S. Perez, I Hope You Fall in Love: Poetry Collection\n|\nI am chic, sleek, and so unique.\n\n- Charles F. Glassman, Brain Drain   The Breakthrough That Will Change Your Life\n|\nWhen comprehending how different people truly are, you also comprehend the absolute necessity of some divine authority.\n\n- Criss Jami, Killosophy\n|\nThe Kingdom of Heaven is within and it lies beyond your wildest imagination, so expect a roller coaster ride to get there!\n\n- Carl Painter, To Be: An Inspiration\n|\nIf your actions don't excite, motivate or inspire others to do better, you're doing it wrong.\n\n- Peprah\n|\nThat lady has a piano.It’s nice, but it’s not the running of riversOr the murmuring trees make ..